sources.title: Fear Falls | Full Movie | Mystery Thriller
sources.description:
Fear Falls - After the tragic death of her parents, a young girl who lives in the small, remote village of Fear Falls must manage her family’s farm on her own. Alone and afraid she stumbles on answers about her parent’s death and begins to uncover a haunting mystery about a creature in the woods surrounding her farm. Now she must face her fear, or fear will be the very thing that devours her, her village, and any hope for tomorrow. Can Fear Falls overcome its name or will fear itself destroy them all?
2022.  Stars: Gary D. Clark, Ashley Hays Wright, Cadence Wright
